data.description: Take a look at this home on a fantastic lot with a paved road and a paved driveway!!!!! Come enjoy this move in ready brand new home on over an acre of land. This lot has nice trees all over it. This home features stainless steel appliances, vinyl flooring throughout, garden bath with soaker tub, separate shower in the master bath. Utility room with a washer and dryer hookup. This home is in sought after St Johns county on a great lot and ready for you!!!!
